            bindings = <
                &kp TILDE   &kp MINUS   &kp HASH   &kp AMPERSAND   &kp PIPE      &kp GRAVE   &kp LCURLY   &kp RCURLY   &kp UNDERSCORE   &kp SEMICOLON
                &kp CARET   &kp PLUS    &kp QUESTION &kp EXCLAMATION &kp DOLLAR    &kp SQT    &kp LPAR    &kp RPAR    &kp LBKT         &kp RBKT
&trans           &kp PERCENT &kp ASTERISK &kp AT_SIGN   &kp COLON      &kp BSLH     &kp DQT    &kp EQUAL   &kp LESS    &kp GREATER      &kp FSLH   &trans
